
What is Label

It is key value pair , it is attached to primitive objects of kubernetes such as
pod
service
node
application: prod
key:value 
1.kubectl label pod <pod-name> <label-key>=<label-value>
2.kubectl label pod mypod environment=production
3.kubectl label pod mypod environment=production app=nginx
This command will add two labels to the pod mypod: environment=production and app=nginx.
4.kubectl describe pod mypod
5.kubectl get pod mypod --show-labels
